
TUÓRUM corda fidélium, Deus miserátor, illústra: et, beátæ Elísabeth précibus gloriósis; fac nos próspera mundi despícere, et cælésti semper consolatióne gaudére. Per Dóminum.
ENLIGHTEN, O God of compassion, the hearts of thy faithful: and, through the glorious prayers of blessed Elizabeth, make us to despise the prosperity of this world, and ever to delight in the consolations of heaven. Through our Lord.
